Breadown/Hiss/Pyro/Injector/Manterror/Stinkbomb/Ramhorn:

::Breakdown, Hiss, and Pyro each turned their heads to Ominous::
"We are just underlings, you have to talk to the boss.  You may follow us for 
now."
::Hiss and Pyro turned back to Quickstrike, hearing the response from the 
obviously in pain arachnid/reptile::
"We don't know its name, the robot hasn't identified itself.  Though, it told 
us that you were in need of repairs, and to escort you to an area.  Though 
the area, was never made clear, so we were hoping you would know."
-----

::Injector hit his back from Teltoli's shots, lowering his stinger launcher 
and firing a missile at her::
"Stupid...Maximal."
::Injector slowly got up, firing off three missiles at the Ark, getting to 
Manterror, and dragging him off towards the Predacon base::
